data.description: Welcome to this cozy 4 bedroom 3 bath home nestled in the desireable Elks Addition of Lewiston. With it's tranquil water feature and inviting patio in a private setting, this place is perfect for those who like to entertain or just enjoy the beauty of nature. As you step inside, you will be greeted by a spacious living area adorned with large windows that flood the space with natural light. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining room and kitchen, creating a warm inviting atmosphere. This home offers the perfect combination of tranquility and convienence. Call today to schedule a tour of this lovely Lewiston home!
